		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=1979"><span id=>HALNineThousand</span></a><b><span id=></span></b><br>2 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=HALNineThousand&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p>This has already been mentioned a few times, but I though I should bring it up anyway. Steamfont is great for Druids level 12-13. Almost all of the mobs around the Minotaur caves are white or blue to you at 12. There is a great deal of danger here, but plenty to kill as well. Be prudent and well-buffed and you will do well here. A rundown of the mobs:<br><br>Rogue clockworks:<br>Easy prey. They seem to spawn more at night. Most of them are level 11, a few are level 12.&nbsp;&nbsp;Pretty crappy loot.<br><br>Harpies:<br>Once again, easy prey. They start the battle with a fire-based spell, so have your Endure Fire up. They tend to be around level 12, and occasionally drop rings which sell for about 1 pp.<br><br>Earth Elementals: Hit pretty hard, but your anti-summoned spells work nicely. No loot at all. Level 12-13.<br><br>Giant Diseased Rats:<br>Level 12-13 as well. They are pretty easy to kill, but have no good loot. They also cast a pretty weak disease spell, nothing to worry about.<br><br>Lesser Ebon Drakes:<br>These guys are all over. Usually level 12-13. Watch out, as when you attack one, the others will help it.<br><br>Minotaur Slavers:<br>Pretty rare. Almost always level 12. Sometimes drop Minotaur Axes, very nice weapons.<br><br>ALWAYS have all of your buffs up when fighting a mob. This includes Strength, Firefist, Treeform, Thistlecoat, Shield of Thistles, and Skin Like Wood. This will save your butt a lot.</p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>======================<br>Would you like to play a game of chess? I play very well.</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
